requesters:
    - signup with approval of the admin
    + campaign creation (with name) (non db)
        + tasks
            + context
            + title
            + keywords
            + choices
        + #workers/task
        + task majority threshold
    - view and modify self own profile (if any)
    + request one campaign report
        + every task with it's result
        + statistics for campaign (quanti task completati, quanti in esecuzione, validi/eseguiti)
        + top 10 workers (with ranking) for campaign

workers:
    + signup
    - profile definition (ex: [musica: 10, arte: 7])
    + view campaigns and apply new campaign
        + tasks request and execution for a campaign
    + view my ranking, executed tasks, valid tasks
